source.name: Almanac API - Ranking by Geography ID within the Nation
source.description: This API is designed to find the rankings by any geography ID within the nation with a specific census metric (population or household) and ranking metric (any of the metrics from provider, demographic, technology or speed). The results are the top ten and bottom ten rankings within the nation for the particular geography type and my area rankings include +/- 5 rankings from the my area rank.
